{"tid":45372,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"岩岩接左隻貓仔，求窗花介紹","createTime":"2016-12-19T02:29:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-22T07:33:07.000Z","uid":42564,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0e8e6d41dac66a26e64f97ebb1fc44b6c82dbe81","tid":45372,"uid":42564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T02:29:17.000Z","msg":"星期六接左隻貓仔返屋企，<br />\n<br />\n問過窗網/窗花嘅問題，<br />\n<br />\n方法1:去日本城或隻家品店買啲格仔掛係窗，不過size 好難就，又麻煩，又唔好睇同唔方便開窗，不過平同可自己整<br />\n<br />\n方法2:  裝窗花，靚啲，方便，俾錢就有人送貨同裝，唔麻煩， 不過貴<br />\n<br />\n咁多位大佬，有冇其他方法？如果冇嘅話可唔可以推介下方法2嘅公司？同埋幾錢左右？上網睇過話300-1000/窗，個價都差幾遠下，細佬我住土瓜灣果頭<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/19/102912_4faf270a4a91d216444be83cbbda7af3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F19%2F102912_4faf270a4a91d216444be83cbbda7af3.jpg&h=8ef87c05&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7q9C1a3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7q9C1a3.jpg&h=fd86a4a9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/19/102914_3be1c8c731367c1324128115f3399c39.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F19%2F102914_3be1c8c731367c1324128115f3399c39.jpg&h=e4d4f99f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8c558f089cc97b1401d22ff1b48dd9ffba21ed52","tid":45372,"uid":65931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T02:33:42.000Z","msg":"窗花都要睇你個窗花有幾密"},{"pid":"55ab470a8208491bab66468e6f62e9d85fd64995","tid":45372,"uid":37651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T02:34:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://world.tmall.com/item/4742731387.htm?spm=a312a.7700714.0.0.5yL0vN\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fworld.tmall.com%2Fitem%2F4742731387.htm%3Fspm%3Da312a.7700714.0.0.5yL0vN&d=aDAjh%2BXfj1h18Xwx2p8ORnvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=0ac48f65\" target=\"_blank\">https://world.tmall.com/item/4742731387.htm?spm=a312a.7700714.0.0.5yL0vN</a><br />\nDIY蚊網,靚仔啲,唔駛搞到屋企好似監倉咁。"},{"pid":"5c4c93cdbcf1359ae3e2945efaf4b45dc0bf5006","tid":45372,"uid":3217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T02:36:32.000Z","msg":"其實窗花都唔見得靚<br />\n好似監獄咁一條條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n窗網，即係好似蚊網個種應該最好睇，但價錢唔知<br />\n<br />\n利申：屋企裝一格格個隻，係五金舖買2.4m x 1.2m都係兩舊水，問佢借埋大剪係個到剪埋"},{"pid":"8ed84a86c3185ec816bfd0ab59efd927cf6ff8ab","tid":45372,"uid":18320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T02:40:41.000Z","msg":"屌你老母留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8512fa9e2a6ec89ba3804758a2693d519458b2a","tid":45372,"uid":42564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T02:57:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://world.tmall.com/item/4742731387.htm?spm=a312a.7700714.0.0.5yL0vN\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fworld.tmall.com%2Fitem%2F4742731387.htm%3Fspm%3Da312a.7700714.0.0.5yL0vN&d=aDAjh%2BXfj1h18Xwx2p8ORnvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=0ac48f65\" target=\"_blank\">https://world.tmall.com/item/4742731387.htm?spm=a312a.7700714.0.0.5yL0vN</a><br />\nDIY蚊網,靚仔啲,唔駛搞到屋企好似監倉咁。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n蚊網有諗過，不過裝左好似會好焗，不過多謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3ca201b7b27b1770865aa5010fa39e2b7d0ca0c","tid":45372,"uid":42564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T03:01:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實窗花都唔見得靚<br />\n好似監獄咁一條條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n窗網，即係好似蚊網個種應該最好睇，但價錢唔知<br />\n<br />\n利申：屋企裝一格格個隻，係五金舖買2.4m x 1.2m都係兩舊水，問佢借埋大剪係個到剪埋</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我見網上都幾多款，係啲條紋會密左，格仔網都睇緊，不過都係可接受嘅，我想多個選擇呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多謝巴打"},{"pid":"2ee4708b07d8b512e7f159f1f9fe329d0013b568","tid":45372,"uid":19895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T03:03:12.000Z","msg":"邏羅貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"246aeafe6452fa4dd7c6ccc1cecd2935ee940869","tid":45372,"uid":19560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T03:04:51.000Z","msg":"比得錢買隻貓就唔爭在比多少少買窗花啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n支持領養代替購買啦好嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"383021df444bd5f84509e233f5ede7010d8456b4","tid":45372,"uid":19560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T03:05:21.000Z","msg":"btw 之前係fb 見到隻透明隱形窗花幾靚"},{"pid":"b2850ab7b6f5a3c5e4fd931b35cde0abb3dcdac1","tid":45372,"uid":42564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T04:26:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邏羅貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSorry 呢隻係布偶仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9100b95068287be74dc4fcbe5f6ec7a7855fe82b","tid":45372,"uid":42564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T04:27:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>比得錢買隻貓就唔爭在比多少少買窗花啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n支持領養代替購買啦好嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n搵緊做窗花公司，大概400/隻，好似貴左啲，所以睇下大家有冇介紹，thanks <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4a590e4bc7cae4be5027746fa7dfa06e8a71880","tid":45372,"uid":21924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T04:41:42.000Z","msg":"以前養隻貓十幾年都未見過佢會跳樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0854368187bfebfc07e65b4e9acee6f1fc4a425b","tid":45372,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl